Thank you for bringing it to our attention; the article has received the corrections.

Answering your question, in formal texts, the ABNT (Associação Brasileira de Normas Técnicas  Brazilian Association of Technical Norms) requires you to write foreign words in italic. It was mistakenly carried to the translation.

Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT);
Dialectical Behavioural Therapy (DBT) 
Selective Serotonin Reuptake Inhibitors (SSRIs).








